OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FA man who admitted trying to kidnap
OL,7,Fchildren in a Cardiff park has been
OL,8,Fordered to remain indefinitely in a
OL,9,Fsecure hospital for ongoing
OL,10,Fpsychiatric treatment.
OL,12,F35-year-old Moynul Janu, from
OL,13,FBangladesh, pleaded guilty in March to
OL,14,Fthree counts of attempting to abduct a
OL,15,Fchild in July 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
