CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FAt a sentencing hearing at Merthyr
OL,7,FCrown Court on Thursday, April 2nd,
OL,8,Fthe court heard Janu approached a
OL,9,Fchild under five playing at the splash
OL,10,Fpad in Victoria Park in July 2025.
OL,11,FJanu touched his leg against the
OL,12,Fchild's leg.
OL,14,FThe child's mother moved her daughter
OL,15,Faway from Janu before approaching the
OL,16,Fmother of a child under 18 months old
OL,17,Falso playing by the water fountain, to
OL,18,Fexplain what had just happened.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FThe court heard that Janu then stood
OL,7,Fbetween the two women and said he was
OL,8,F"grabbing the kids".
OL,10,FHe took hold of both children by their
OL,11,Farms, but let go and walked off after
OL,12,Ftheir mothers shouted at him.
OL,14,FThe court heard that Janu told park
OL,15,Fstaff he was homeless in the UK but
OL,16,Fwas looking for a job and had a wife
OL,17,Fand children in Bangladesh.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
