PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FJanu, who has no previous convictions,
OL,7,Fwas detained at the scene and given a
OL,8,Flift away from the park to the city
OL,9,Fcentre, but was not taken into custody.
OL,11,FA witness statement on behalf of one
OL,12,Fof the children's mothers was read to
OL,13,Fthe court, where she said her daughter
OL,14,Fwas vulnerable and lives with
OL,15,Fdisabilities.
OL,17,F"I am still shocked and astonished
OL,18,Fthat someone could think he could take
OL,19,Fa child like that", the statement said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
