CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FShe said her daughter has woken up
OL,7,Fscreaming in the night following the
OL,8,Fincident, fearing that Janu was coming
OL,9,Fto get her.
OL,11,FThe victim's mother described the
OL,12,Femotional strain as "unimaginable".
OL,13,FThe other victim's mother told the
OL,14,Fcourt in a statement that she will
OL,15,F"struggle to overcome this horrific
OL,16,Fexperience".
OL,26,@tD@UOUtD@bO]wD@AOUxD@KO]
