PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FThe following day, on July 4th 2025,
OL,7,FJanu was seen outside a nursery in the
OL,8,FBridgend area. A staff member said she
OL,9,Fthought he might be enquiring about
OL,10,Fchildcare, but then panicked when he
OL,11,Fstarted approaching her very quickly.
OL,13,FAs she retreated inside, the nursery
OL,14,Fdoors locked automatically, but Janu
OL,15,Fbegan pressing buttons and trying to
OL,16,Fguess the code. The court heard that
OL,17,F17 children were in the nursery at the
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,20,FPolice then arrested Janu nearby.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
