FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FThe court heard Janu was living with
OL,7,Fbipolar affective disorder before and
OL,8,Fduring the incident, for which he is
OL,9,Fnow receiving treatment. The court
OL,10,Fheard he has a complex history of
OL,11,Fmental health issues.
OL,13,FAfter his arrest, Janu was remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody at HMP Cardiff before being
OL,15,Fmoved to a secure psychiatric hospital
OL,16,Fin England.
OL,18,FHis Honour Judge Kember said he had
OL,19,Fconsidered the evidence of two doctors
OL,20,Finstructed to assess Janu under the
OL,21,FMental Health Act.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
