PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775153467
OL,3,CMan who tried to kidnap children in
OL,4,Cplay park sentenced
OL,6,FHe said that both doctors are of the
OL,7,Fopinion that Janu needs to be detained
OL,8,Fin a secure hospital facility until it
OL,9,Fis determined he is safe to be
OL,10,Freleased.
